ght:1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size:19px;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:normal;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></span></p>\n\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:19px; line-height:1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size:19px;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><a href=\"https://medium.com/with-liberty/a-gay-fashion-designer-for-the-pope-world-peace-and-inadvertent-fasting-e9a73601fe25\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:normal;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Three Papacies&#39; Openly Gay Fashion Designer</span></a></span></span></p>\n\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:19px; line-height:1.75em;\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:19px; line-height:1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size:19px;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><a href=\"https://heathermedwards.substack.com/p/a-new-pope-and-old-wounds-indigenous\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:normal;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">​&quot;A New Pope and Old Wounds&quot;; Indigenous Perspectives I Needed to Read​​</span></a></span></span></p>\n\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:19px; line-height:1.75em;\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:19px; line-height:1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size:19px;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><a href=\"https://heathermedwards.substack.com/p/a-rapper-the-pope-and-the-quakers\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:normal;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Doechii, the Pope, and the Quakers​</span></a></span></span></p>\n\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:19px; line-height:1.75em;\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:19px; line-height:1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size:19px;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><a href=\"https://heathermedwards.substack.com/p/christians-are-called-to-be-dangerous?utm_source=profile&utm_medium=reader2\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:normal;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&quot;Christians Are Called to Be Dangerous&quot;​​</span></a></span></span></p>\n\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:19px; line-height:1.75em;\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:19px; line-height:1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size:19px;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><a href=\"https://medium.com/with-liberty/no-catholics-do-not-love-ai-pope-trump-bc8fb41fe849\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:normal;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">No, Catholics Do Not Love AI Pope Trump</span></a></span></span></p>\n\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:19px; line-height:1.75em;\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:19px; line-height:1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size:19px;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><a href=\"https://medium.com/with-liberty/ice-shoots-a-praying-pastor-the-pope-calls-us-to-care-for-migrants-refugees-and-one-another-11464b50886f\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:normal;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">​​ICE Shoots a Praying Pastor, the Pope Calls Us to Love and Serve Migrants, Refugees, and One Another</span></a></span></span></p>\n\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:19px; line-height:1.75em;\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:19px; line-height:1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size:19px;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><a href=\"https://heathermedwards.substack.com/p/ice-cbp-are-not-responding-to-a-holy?utm_source=profile&utm_medium=reader2\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:normal;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">​ICE Is not Fighting a Holy War, They&#39;re Creating a Human Rights Crisis </span></a></span></span></p>\n\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:19px; line-height:1.75em;\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:19px; line-height:1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size:19px;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><a href=\"https://heathermedwards.substack.com/p/daredevil-and-performative-catholicism?utm_source=profile&utm_medium=reader2\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:normal;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">​​Daredevil and Performative Catholicism in American Politics</span></a></span></span></p>\n\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:19px; line-height:1.75em;\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:19px; line-height:1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size:19px;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><a href=\"https://heathermedwards.substack.com/p/my-fellow-christians-vote-from-your?utm_source=profile&utm_medium=reader2\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:normal;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">​My Fellow Christians, Vote From Your Heart, Even if it Means Voting &quot;Against&quot; Your Church​</span></a></span></span></p>\n\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:19px; line-height:1.75em;\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:19px; line-height:1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size:19px;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><a href=\"https://heathermedwards.substack.com/p/pope-francis-and-taylor-swift-arent\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:normal;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Taylor Swift and Pope Francis Aren&#39;t Staying Silent</span></a></span></span></p>\n\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:19px; line-height:1.75em;\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:19px; line-height:1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size:19px;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:normal;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">​<span style=\"text-decoration:underline;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><a href=\"https://heathermedwards.substack.com/p/the-theater-of-hypocrisy-and-holy?utm_source=profile&utm_medium=reader2\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Holy Resistance to the Theater of Hypocrisy</a></span></span></span></p>","skin":"WRichTextThemeSkin","isQaMode":false,"fullNameCompType":"wysiwyg.viewer.components.WRichText"},"comp-mijg9elw":{"html":"<h5 class=\"font_5 wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:24px;\">Published in Interfaith Now</h5>\n\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:19px; line-height:1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size:19px;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:normal;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></span></p>\n\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:19px; line-height:1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size:19px;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><a href=\"https://medium.com/interfaith-now/god-bless-the-religious-faithful-suing-the-maga-administration-57d47f26a83f\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:normal;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">God Bless the Religious Faithful Suing the MAGA Administration </span></a></span></span></p>\n\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:19px; line-height:1.75em;\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:19px; line-height:1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size:19px;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><a href=\"https://medium.com/interfaith-now/catholics-we-are-called-to-help-immigrants-in-ice-detention-1202478b7679?postPublishedType=repub\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:normal;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Catholics: We Are Called to Help Immigrants in ICE Detention</span></a></span></span></p>\n\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:19px; line-height:1.75em;\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:19px; line-height:1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size:19px;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><a href=\"https://medium.com/interfaith-now/the-catholic-nuns-and-priests-fighting-for-vulnerable-people-d31381872ae6\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:normal;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">​The Catholic Nuns and Priests Fighting for Vulnerable People​</span></a></span></span></p>\n\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:19px; line-height:1.75em;\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:19px; line-height:1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size:19px;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><a href=\"https://medium.com/interfaith-now/why-the-pope-died-with-only-100-to-his-name-9b7fbf976c48\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:normal;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Why the Pope Died with Only $100 to his Name​</span></a></span></span></p>\n\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:19px; line-height:1.75em;\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:19px; line-height:1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size:19px;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><a href=\"https://medium.com/interfaith-now/christian-leaders-petitioning-ice-for-humane-treatment-of-our-brothers-and-sisters-are-denied-15681cb21c9c\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:normal;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">The Christian Leaders Petitioning ICE for Humane Treatment of Our Brothers and Sisters​​</span></a></span></span></p>\n\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:19px; line-height:1.75em;\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:19px; line-height:1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size:19px;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><a href=\"https://medium.com/interfaith-now/the-world-lost-a-peacemaker-today-b4dc2f5e7e8d\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:normal;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">&quot;The World Lost a Peacemaker Today&quot;</span></a></span></span></p>\n\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:19px; line-height:1.75em;\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:19px; line-height:1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size:19px;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><a href=\"https://medium.com/interfaith-now/praying-with-my-parents-election-night-2024-876189e852bf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:normal;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">​Praying With My Parents, Election Night 2024​</span></a></span></span></p>\n\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:19px; line-height:1.75em;\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:19px; line-height:1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size:19px;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><a href=\"https://medium.com/interfaith-now/reconciling-faith-with-politics-bible-verses-you-cant-misinterpret-3b35a6955c5a\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:normal;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Reconciling Faith with Politics: </span></a></span></span><span style=\"font-size:19px;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><a href=\"https://medium.com/interfaith-now/reconciling-faith-with-politics-bible-verses-you-cant-misinterpret-3b35a6955c5a\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:normal;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Bible Verses You Can&rsquo;t Misinterpret​​</span></a></span></span></p>","skin